to start the backend(node server) please execute 
 node .\app.js   
 I created a demon on package.json to run the node server:
     "dev": "nodemon src/index.js"
     just execute:
* npm run dev 
 without quotes on mern folder, this command will auto update the backend when detect changes on sourcecode

 index.js se encarga del front
 app.js se encarga del backend

 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 to start front-end 
 move to mern/client folder and run:
 * npm run dev